video.title: Power Rangers Dino Charge
video.synopsis: In the time of dinosaurs, the ancient and powerful Energems were lost on Earth, and now the evil bounty hunter Sledge has returned to find them.

episodes.synopsis: Millions of years after the mysterious Energems were entrusted to the dinosaurs, courageous teens find two of the long-lost, precious artifacts.
episodes.title: Powers from the Past

episodes.synopsis: A new teen bonds with an Energem and joins Tyler and Shelby on their journey to the Dinosaur Museum, where they learn they are now Power Rangers.
episodes.title: Past, Present and Fusion

episodes.synopsis: After Sledge arrives on Earth, the newly formed Ranger team is compromised when Tyler goes off on his own, against the wishes of the other Rangers.
episodes.title: A Fool’s Hour

episodes.synopsis: Chase tries to help Koda adapt to modern technology when he struggles to ride their new Dino Cycles, but later Koda's caveman instincts save the day.
episodes.title: Return of the Caveman

episodes.synopsis: When a Maori fortune teller asks him for help guarding her shop from a potential thief, Chase falls under the spell of Sledge's latest monster.
episodes.title: Breaking Black

episodes.synopsis: When the fast-firing monster Cavity attacks Amber Beach, Riley thinks that Chase doesn't take the threat seriously enough.
episodes.title: The Tooth Hurts

episodes.synopsis: Thanks to Shelby and Kendall's latest invention, the Rangers close in on the Ankylo Zord, but Fury and Sledge conspire to steal it for themselves.
episodes.title: Let Sleeping Zords Lie

episodes.synopsis: When Ranger clones steal the real Rangers' irreplaceable tracking device, Fury learns the location of the powerful Ptera Zord.
episodes.title: Double Ranger, Double Danger

episodes.synopsis: Riley's logical mind is put to the ultimate puzzle-solving test when the Rangers are trapped in a real-life maze by Fury and one of his henchmen.
episodes.title: When Logic Fails

episodes.synopsis: Discovering the Gold Energem in an exhibit on loan from the nation of Zandar, Shelby and Tyler impersonate Zandar royalty to lure Fury into a trap.
episodes.title: The Royal Rangers

episodes.synopsis: Koda and the Rangers fight to save an arrogant prince and the Gold Energem from Fury, but a powerful 800-year-old knight seizes the jewel for himself.
episodes.title: Breakout

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers cannot prove themselves worthy of their newest ally, the Gold Ranger, when one of Sledge's monsters steals their courage.
episodes.title: Knight after Knights

episodes.synopsis: A playful rivalry between Tyler and Ivan interferes with the Rangers' efforts to find and defuse a bomb that Sledge's monsters have planted.
episodes.title: Sync or Swim

episodes.synopsis: When three Rangers become trapped in an underground tomb, it's a race against time for Chase to master his new power upgrade and save his friends.
episodes.title: True Black

episodes.synopsis: Prince Phillip discovers money can't buy the respect of an Energem when he embarks on his own quest to become a Power Ranger.
episodes.title: Rise of a Ranger

episodes.synopsis: When one of Sledge's monsters breaks up the Rangers' friendship, it's up to Riley and Koda to remind the team what they truly mean to each other.
episodes.title: No Matter How You Slice It

episodes.synopsis: When one of Sledge's transport pods is spotted in New Zealand, the Rangers head to Auckland and are shocked to discover the existence of a new Ranger.
episodes.title: World Famous! (In New Zealand)

episodes.synopsis: With the Purple Energem in hand, the Rangers race to find the Purple Plesio Zord before Sledge can destroy it for good.
episodes.title: Deep Down Under

episodes.synopsis: While searching for a new Purple Ranger, the teens find all their personal wishes coming true -- but in the worst possible way.
episodes.title: Wishing for a Hero

episodes.synopsis: With two Energems now in Sledge's possession, the Rangers and Kendall must take the fight to his ship in order to save the world.
episodes.title: One More Energem

episodes.synopsis: When a monster kidnaps and takes on the appearance of a Ranger during a Halloween party, Kendall must discover which team member is the fake.
episodes.title: The Ghostest with the Mostest

episodes.synopsis: When Poisandra steals Santa's tablet, the Rangers must get it back before Christmas.
episodes.title: Race to Rescue Christmas
